summary: Start the game with a premade Nord character.
descriptionHtml:
This is the female nord that I have been questing with for ~50 hours now. I still like how she looks with everything so I decided to let some of you share the character. It appears i got impaled by an arrow in the first image!

Mods used
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=26 - Detailed Faces \"V1\"
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=30 - No More Blocky Faces

You should be able to modify the character further by adding tattoos and the such from using ~ player.showracemenu

Note: This will not start you directly at the start but 30 seconds and into the first door you would rush to. Watch the start if you haven\'t done so.

Let me know what you think of the character. Your criticism, good or bad is appreciated!
author: lFlapjackl
